    h2 Checkbox Layout
    p Checkbox layout is pretty simple:
    :code(lang="html")
          <!-- checkbox element -->
          <label class="checkbox">
            <!-- checkbox input -->
            <input type="checkbox">
            <!-- checkbox icon -->
            <i class="icon-checkbox"></i>
          </label>
    h2 Checkbox Group/List
    p To create Checkbox group/list we need to use <a href="list-view.html">List View</a> with few additions:
    :code(lang="html")
          <div class="list">
            <ul>
              <!-- Single checkbox item -->
              <li>
                <label class="item-checkbox item-content">
                  <!-- Checkbox input -->
                  <input type="checkbox"/>
                  <!-- Checkbox icon -->
                  <i class="icon icon-checkbox"></i>
                  <div class="item-inner">
                    <!-- Checkbox Title -->
                    <div class="item-title">Books</div>
                  </div>
                </label>
              </li>
              <!-- Another checkbox item -->
              <li>
                <label class="item-checkbox item-content">
                  <!-- Checked by default -->
                  <input type="checkbox" checked/>
                  <i class="icon icon-checkbox"></i>
                  <div class="item-inner">
                    <div class="item-title">Music</div>
                  </div>
                </label>
              </li>
              ...
            </ul>
          </div>
    .important-note
      ul
        li <code>item-content</code> must be a <code><b>&lt;label&gt;</b></code> element with additional <code><b>item-checkbox</b></code> class
        li Checkbox input (<code>&lt;input type="checkbox"&gt;</code>) must be a first child of <code>item-content</code>
        li Checkbox icon must be <b>after</b> checkbox input
